         The proposed project (the Project) consists of a senior revolving loan to an SPV managed by Barak Fund Management Ltd (Barak) to provide trade and commodity finance to enterprises operating in Africa. The loan proceeds would invest alongside Barak's short-term African trade and commodity funds; the Project will focus primarily on supporting SMEs in the agricultural sector, although other sectors, such as consumer goods, will also be financed.

